data.description: Step into refined living where the residence seamlessly accommodates evolving needs. An additional living space, thoughtfully attached, caters to a growing teen seeking independence or provides a haven for family and friends. Traverse the inviting entrance to a generous living space adorned with a captivating fireplace, casting a warm glow. Glance through windows to be captivated by panoramic views of your expansive 5-acre domain, a picturesque backdrop to daily life. Versatility takes center stage with a bedroom doubling as a meticulously designed office space. The kitchen, a culinary haven, boasts a built-in cooktop on the island, transitioning seamlessly into the adjacent breakfast area—a haven for casual dining and entertaining guests. Don't miss the opportunity to experience this idyllic lifestyle. Schedule your showing today and witness firsthand the allure of this countryside—your journey to tranquility awaits.
